						<summary>

						<p>On a rock in the field.</p>						

						<p>Veṅkaṭapati II, 1633 A.D.</p>						

						<p>The record is badly damaged. It is dated in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1555, Śrīmukha,</hi> the other details being lost. The Śaka year corresponds to <hi rend="bold">1633 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It seems to record a <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> gift probably of land. The details are lost.</p>						

						</summary>
